notes: West Indies 50 in 9.1 overs (Wavell Hinds 8, Chris Gayle 35)
West Indies 100 in 16.6 overs (Wavell Hinds 36, Brian Lara 2)
West Indies 250 in 44.3 overs (Wavell Hinds 125, Chanderpaul 2)
Rain stopped play after 45 overs in WI innings, no resumption.
50 run Partnership between Taibu and Ervine in 61 balls
FH Edwards took a wicket with his first ball in ODI's.
Edwards's figures were the best for any debutant in ODI's.
WW Hinds scored his 4th ODI 100, and his highest score

stories.title: Dream debut by Edwards helps West Indies level series
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v West Indies, 4th ODI, Harare
stories.summary: Six wickets on his one-day debut by Fidel Edwards, along with a century by Wavell Hinds, helped West Indies to a comfortable 72-run win against Zimbabwe in the 4th one-dayer at Harare.
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by John Ward
